static int[] burbuja(int[] vector) {
    for (int i = 0; i < vector.length; i++) {
        for (int j = 0; j < vector.length-i-1; j++) {
            if (vector[j] > vector[j+1]) {
                int aux = vector[j];
                vector[j] = vector[j+1];
                vector[j+1] = aux;
            }
        }
    }
    return vector;
}

Complejidad: O(n^2).

Algoritmo de ordenacion mas rapido (divide y venceras).

static void quicksort(int[] arr, int izq, int der) {
    int pivote = arr[izq];
    int i=izq, j=der, aux;
    while (i < j) {
        while (arr[i] <= pivote && i < j) i++;
        while (arr[j] > pivote) j--;
        if (i < j) { aux=arr[i]; arr[i]=arr[j]; arr[j]=aux; }
    }
    arr[izq] = arr[j];
    arr[j] = pivote;
    if (izq < j-1) quicksort(arr, izq, j-1);
    if (j+1 < der) quicksort(arr, j+1, der);
}

Complejidad: O(n log n) promedio.

